title: Beginning our shit car offroad adventure!
description: This week the guys are in Phoenix preparing to embark on the adventure that will become All Cars Go To Heaven 2. A day of wandering through the blistering Phoenix heat was spent finding cars for the trip. In addition to the beater cars. In addition John Bothwell of PurSang will be joining the guys in his Model T and they discuss the mods necessary for it to survive this trip.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
